{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by classic local multiplayer brawlers, <i>Duel &amp; Trial</i> is a fast-paced party game that supports 2-4 players, packed with chaotic fun and unexpected twists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players battle it out in rooms filled with portals and traps, using a variety of items unlocked from treasure chests to outwit and defeat each other. The last player standing wins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With simple yet challenging mechanics, mastering the game requires skill and practice. Want to pull off flashy moves? You\u2019ll need to train your reflexes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perfect for friends to gather around and play together. Struggling in the game? Settle it in real life with a friendly push!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features both <i>Duel</i> and <i>Trial</i> modes, allowing players to choose how they want to challenge themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A mysterious and immersive world setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fun and unique character designs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Various treasure chests and rewards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple battle arenas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Creative items that can change the course of the game</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3431170?t=1739605931","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3431170/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739605931","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3431170/2efbca0d20a6a3cb8f95ed58f1a75e39b2b6b661/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739605931","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3431170/2efbca0d20a6a3cb8f95ed58f1a75e39b2b6b661/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739605931","categories":[{"descri